Say '''Matalom''' et kumatlo ya klase baley ed luyag na [[Leyte]], [[Pilipinas]]. Unong ed 2010 Census, say papulasyon to et 31,097 totoo. Walay kabaleg tan sukat to ya 132 sq. km. Sikato et walad kumalima ya distrito. Say zip code to et 6526.	
															
